    /// is a bit faster than this method `modular_mul()`.
    /// So, if `rhs` is primitive unsigned integral data type such as u8, u16,
    /// u32, u64, and u128, use the method
    /// [modular_mul_uint()](struct@BigUInt#method.modular_mul_uint).
