    ///   return value will be set and the result value will have the value `0`.
    /// - In summary, the result value and its flags will be set as follows:
    /// 
    /// | `modulo` | result value (self) | flags       |
    /// |----------|---------------------|-------------|
    /// | 0 or 1   | 0                   | `UNDEFINED` |
    /// 
