    /// Divides (`self` % `modulo`) by (`rhs` % `modulo`),
    /// and returns the quotient.
    /// 
    /// # Arguments
    /// - `rhs` divides `self`, and is of `&Self` type.
    /// - `modulo` is the divisor to divide the remainder of (`self` / `rhs`),
    ///   and is of `&Self` type.
